{"tid":750771,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[疑問]關於旅行買手信","createTime":"2018-07-21T08:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T09:52:25.000Z","uid":108668,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ebb62d5e5f471ad2acbaf470465983ef7b7d6cc","tid":750771,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟日前走咗去台北玩四日 <br />\n基本上都係同台灣<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[black]妹子[/black]</span>朋友一齊四圍去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都冇乜點買手信<br />\n咁最後一日走嘅時候就隨手執咗啲嘢返香港諗住自己食 同埋拎啲返公司畀班餓鬼<br />\n因為公司每個餓鬼去旅行都帶一大包嘢食返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我都養成呢個習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁返到屋企我拎咗包豬肉乾出嚟食 畀我家姐望到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當期時佢就冇咩反應<br />\n<br />\n但幾日之後我聽到佢同我老母講<br />\n話我去旅行買啲手信影都冇<br />\n淨係見過包豬肉乾仲要好快唔見曬<br />\n重覆不下十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日我拎幾包嘢返公司<br />\n佢又再同我講多次<br />\n話我啲手信買返嚟唔係畀我地食嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心諗做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴絲覺得<br />\n去旅行買手信畀屋企人係咪應份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢覺得買手信係理所當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮 : 屌你老母自己辛苦賺錢去轉旅行家下奉旨買手信畀你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負皮 : 話曬都屋企人 緊係要畀手信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e2413c38bdaa82c4bb86afe5ebf6a4091ae935","tid":750771,"uid":47041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"咁都要開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想咪買<br />\n唔想咪算lor<br />\n你屋企人介意下次咪買lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}